
'''''The Constant Gardener''''' ni filim iri ituruka muri England and German yasohotse muri 2005 iyoborwa na  Fernando Meirelles . Amashusho yakozwe na Jeffrey Caine ashingiye ku gitabo cya John le Carré cyo mu 2001 cyitwa <nowiki><i><b>The Constant Gardener</b></nowiki><nowiki></i></nowiki> . Iyi nkuru ikurikira Justin Quayle ( Ralph Fiennes ), umudipolomate w’Ubwongereza muri Kenya, ubwo yageragezaga gukemura ikibazo cy’iyicwa ry’umugore we Tessa ( Rachel Weisz ), uharanira Amnesty, asimburana n’ibintu byinshi byerekana amateka y’urukundo rwabo.

Iyi filime yafatiwe amashusho ahitwa Loiyangalani no mucyaro cya Kibera, igice cya [[Nairobi]], muri [[Kenya]] . Ibintu muri kariya gace byagize ingaruka ku bakinnyi ndetse no ku bakozi ku buryo bashizeho Constant Gardener Trust kugira ngo batange uburezi bw'ibanze kuri iyo midugudu. Uyu mugambi washingiye ku buryo budasobanutse ku rubanza rwabayeho i Kano, muri Nijeriya . Impapuro za DVD zasohotse muri Amerika ku ya 1 Mutarama 2006 no mu Bwongereza ku ya 13 Werurwe 2006. Ubwitonzi bwa Justin ariko bwitondewe kubihingwa bye ninsanganyamatsiko yagarukaga, aho ishusho ya firime yakomotse. Hubert Koundé, Danny Huston, Bill Nighy, Pete Postlethwaite, na Donald Sumpter bakoranye. Iyi filime yagenze neza kandi yinjiza amafaranga menshi kandi yegukana ibihembo bine bya Oscar, yegukana umukinnyi wa filime witwaye neza muri Rachel Weisz.

